data.description: Discover the perfect blend of nature and comfort in this inviting 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home nestled on 1.41 acres of lush, wooded beauty in the sought-after Crumbacher community. This charming residence, built in the year 2000, offers the ideal sanctuary for those seeking privacy and tranquility while still being conveniently close to all the amenities you desire.  With 1,848 square feet of living space, there's room for everyone to spread out and relax.  Your vehicles and storage needs are taken care of with a spacious 2-car garage.  Multiple outbuildings on the property offer endless possibilities for workshops, storage, or creative endeavors.    Don't miss the Virtual tour and 3D walkthrough!
